PCRE2_SET_RECURSION_LIMIT(3Library Functions ManuaPCRE2_SET_RECURSION_LIMIT(3)

NAME
       PCRE2 - Perl-compatible regular expressions (revised API)

SYNOPSIS

       #include <pcre2.h>

       int pcre2_set_recursion_limit(pcre2_match_context *mcontext,
         uint32_t value);

DESCRIPTION

       This  function  is  obsolete  and  should  not be used in new code. Use
       pcre2_set_depth_limit() instead.

       There is a complete description of the PCRE2 native API in the pcre2api
       page and a description of the POSIX API in the pcre2posix page.

PCRE2 10.30                      25 March 2017    PCRE2_SET_RECURSION_LIMIT(3)
